FORMAT: 1A
HOST: http://company-database.herokuapp.com

# Company Database -app
Company API is a small database application to store company addresses and info about 
directors and owners.

# Group Company

## Company [/companies/{company_id}]
A single Company object with all its details

+ Parameters
    + company_id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Company to perform action with. Has example value.

+ Model (application/json)

    JSON representation of Company Resource.

    + Body

            {
                "company" : {
                    "id"         : 10,
                    "created_at" : "2014-03-07T12:48:15+01:00",
                    "updated_at" : "2014-03-09T23:39:37+01:00",
                    "avatar_url" : "http://uri.com/img.jpg",
                    "name"       : "Mogensen Consulting",
                    "phone"      : "98989898",
                    "email"      : "Frede@server-1.dk",
                    "city"       : "Aarhus C",
                    "address"    : "Langelandsgade 9",
                    "country"    : "Danmark"
                }
            }


### Retrieve a Company [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    [Company][]

### Upate a company [PUT]
To update a Company send a JSON with updated value for one or more
of the Company resource attributes.
All attributes values (states) from the previous version of this
Company are carried over by default if not included in the hash.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "name": "Updated company name"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    [Company][]

### Remove a Company [DELETE]
+ Response 204

