## Director [/companies/{company_id}/directors/{director_id}]
A single Director object with all its details belonging to a specific Company

+ Parameters
    + company_id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Company to perform action with. Has example value.
    + director_id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Director to perform action with. Has example value.
    
+ Model (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                "director" : {
                    "name"       : "Jane Doe",
                    "phone"      : "98989898",
                    "email"      : "Jane@Doe.com",
                    "city"       : "Aarhus C",
                    "address"    : "Directors Street 9",
                    "country"    : "Danmark"
                }
            }

### Retrieve a Director [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    [Director][]

### Upate a Director [PUT]
Post a json request with any of the following attributes, to update
the director info.

+ Request (application/json)

    [Director][]


+ Response 200 (application/json;charset=utf-8)

    [Director][]

### Remove a Director [DELETE]
+ Response 204

